rows.label: qst000905_msg0001
rows.name:
Thank you so much!
Good to see this little fella back in one
piece.

rows.label: qst000905_msg0002
rows.name:
It's been a real lesson, this. We know
how much we need to improve now.

rows.label: qst000905_msg0003
rows.name:
It's sad to say, but we really bit off
more than we could chew.

rows.label: qst000905_msg0004
rows.name:
If we can't even handle a few Ignas,
it's going to be a long time before
our names ring out in Invidia...

rows.label: qst000905_msg0005
rows.name:
But there was one good thing
that came from all this!

rows.label: qst000905_msg0006
rows.name:
Dororo says he's going to invest
in our mercenary band!

rows.label: qst000905_msg0007
rows.name:
We'll do everything we can to make
sure his money doesn't go to waste!

rows.label: qst000905_msg0008
rows.name:
Which reminds me - we want
you to have this.

rows.label: qst000905_msg0009
rows.name:
It's our fee from Dororo for
this job. You guys are the ones
that really earned it.

rows.label: qst000905_msg0010
rows.name: We'd be honored if you'd accept it.

rows.label: qst000905_msg0011
rows.name:
Nah, we're the ones that should be
saying thank you.

rows.label: qst000905_msg0012
rows.name:
This whole mess taught us exactly how
strong we need to get. As strong as you
guys!
